Dialogue: 4,0:02:53.77,0:02:58.99,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(400,400)}それは愛しすぎる
Dialogue: 5,0:02:58.57,0:03:03.74,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(400,400)}魔法のキーワード
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:57.01,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(400,400)}错开的话语背后
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.42,0:02:02.68,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(400,400)}藏着封锁心门的钥匙
Dialogue: 2,0:02:02.26,0:02:07.31,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(400,400)}若是解除那名为你的标识
Dialogue: 3,0:02:06.72,0:02:12.90,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(400,400)}就能拯救那笑容的话
Dialogue: 4,0:02:12.61,0:02:15.82,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(400,400)}邀请夏日的狂风
Dialogue: 5,0:02:15.28,0:02:18.49,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(400,400)}和白天的疾风骤雨
Dialogue: 6,0:02:18.44,0:02:23.20,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(400,400)}波长同步
Dialogue: 7,0:02:22.87,0:02:26.08,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(400,400)}虽然无法浪漫地
Dialogue: 8,0:02:25.62,0:02:31.21,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(400,400)}说出动听的话语
Dialogue: 9,0:02:30.83,0:02:37.80,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(400,400)}但我们的目标仍是那片蓝天──
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:42.68,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(400,400)}我们能够成为一体
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.18,0:02:48.18,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(400,400)}不知所措的泪水与梦想
Dialogue: 2,0:02:47.60,0:02:54.40,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(400,400)}都会被真实所吸引
